# Select who to add to the new Public Stream or Direct Message

To get started being present with people online, you first need to sort out who that is going to be.

We've made it super easy to create a new stream by clicking on your friend's names and adding as many as you like to the stream. You'll see each time you click a name it appears as a little chip. You can remove someone by clicking the cross near their name.

Click someone's name and their chip is added to the list people in the Stream and the filter is cleared. Filter the list again and click someone\'s name to add their chip too.

Click the "Be Present" button to create your new stream and start the Chat.

Remove someone by clicking the cross near their name.
